text: Gustav Kaufmann (23 August 1918 - 20 January 2015) was a Liechtenstein sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Liechtenstein male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Liechtenstein Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
